AFT Firmware Update
===================


Latest Firmware Files
---------------------

Latest AFT firmware updates are located at

	ftp.sangoma.com/linux/current_wanpipe/firmware


Save the latest BIN files into the current (wan_aftup/)
directory, and proceed with wanpipe firmware update.


Updating AFT Firmware 
---------------------

1) Make sure wanpipe is unloaded 

	wanrouter stop		

	wanrouter modules #No modules loaded in kernel


2) Start update program

	./update_aft_firm.sh


		Specify interface name that corresponds 
		to your AFT card.


		Select firmware latest firmware version

		Once the flashing is done, select Y to reload firmware.
		(This step only reloads flash, not your machine!)


		Card is ready for normal operation. 
		(No reboot needed)
	


